   132	## Token 매핑
   133	
   134	`tablist.yaml`의 root·indicator 슬롯 토큰. recipe variant(size·layout)로만 제어하고, 하드 CSS 덮어쓰기 금지.
   135	
   136	```
   137	tablist recipe (List 컨테이너):
   138	  root.color:             $color.bg.layer-default
   139	  root.strokeBottomWidth: 1px
   140	  root.strokeColor:       $color.stroke.neutral-muted
   141	
   142	  layout=hug:
   143	    root.paddingX:        $dimension.spacing-x.global-gutter
   144	    indicator.insetX:     0px
   145	  layout=fill:
   146	    root.paddingX:        0px
   147	    indicator.insetX:     $dimension.spacing-x.global-gutter
   148	
   149	  size=small:
   150	    root.height:          40px
   151	  size=medium:
   152	    root.height:          44px
   153	
   154	tablist recipe (Indicator):
   155	  indicator.height:              2px
   156	  indicator.color:               $color.fg.neutral
   157	  indicator.transformDuration:   $duration.d4        ← D4 트랜지션
   158	  indicator.transformTimingFunction: $timing-function.easing
   159	```
   160	
   161	> `indicator.transformDuration = $duration.d4`: Indicator가 선택 탭 위치로 슬라이드하는 트랜지션 속도. CSS `transform`에만 적용되며 `transition: transform $duration.d4 $timing-function.easing` 으로 구현된다.
